# ğŸ”¹ 1ï¸âƒ£3ï¸âƒ£ Equality & Hashing

```java
equals(Object o)
hashCode()
```

Two lists are equal if:

* Same size
* Same elements
* Same order

---

# ğŸ”¹ 1ï¸âƒ£4ï¸âƒ£ Java 8+ Stream Support

