# ğŸ“Œ Most Important Methods (Interview Focus)

| Category | Methods                    |
| -------- | -------------------------- |
| Add      | `add`, `addAll`            |
| Access   | `get`                      |
| Remove   | `remove`, `clear`          |
| Search   | `contains`, `indexOf`      |
| Modify   | `set`                      |
| Size     | `size`, `isEmpty`          |
| Sort     | `sort`, `Collections.sort` |
| Iterate  | `iterator`, for-each       |

---

# ğŸ§  Time Complexity Summary (VERY IMPORTANT)

| Operation         | Time               |
| ----------------- | ------------------ |
| Access (get/set)  | **O(1)**           |
| Add at end        | **O(1)** amortized |
| Add/remove middle | **O(n)**           |
| Search            | **O(n)**           |
| Iteration         | **O(n)**           |

---

# ğŸ”‘ Mental Model (Lock This In)

> **ArrayList = Dynamic Array**
> Fast access, slow middle insertion/removal.


